---
title: Montreal Bistro Grilled Steak with Garlicky Mushrooms, Potatoes and Side Salad
description: This French-inspired meal is best enjoyed outside, fresh off the grill! Mushrooms soak up rich butter, savoury soy, herby thyme and garlic in a foil pouch for easy clean-up.
